# OpenCoreSDK 架构分析

## 1. 项目概述

OpenCoreSDK 是一个 Android 原生崩溃转储（coredump）SDK，支持 Java 层和 Native 层 crash捕获，生成 ELF 格式的 core dump 文件，供 `core-parser` 工具分析。

- **GitHub**: https://github.com/Penguin38/OpenCoreSDK
- **版本**: 1.4.16
- **架构支持**: arm64, arm, x86_64, x86, riscv64, lp32 (32-bit)
- **核心语言**: Java (API层) + C++ (Native核心)

---

## 2. 六层分层结构

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "UI Layer (Java)"
        A["Coredump.java<br/>JavaCrashHandler"]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer (Java JNI Bridge)"
        B["Coredump.java<br/>native* methods"]
    end

    subgraph "JNI Bridge (C++)"
        C["opencore_jni.cpp<br/>JNI Methods"]
    end

    subgraph "Native Core (C++)"
        D["opencore.cpp<br/>Opencore Class"]
    end

    subgraph "Config Layer"
        E["build.gradle<br/>CMakeLists.txt"]
    end

    subgraph "Test Layer"
        F["ExampleUnitTest<br/>ExampleInstrumentedTest"]
    end

    A -->|"enable/disable"| A
    A -->|"doCoredump()"| B
    B -->|"JNI Call"| C
    C -->|"Opencore::API"| D
```

### 层级详细说明

| 层级 | 文件 | 职责 |
|------|------|------|
| **UI Layer** | `Coredump.java` | 对外暴露的 Java API，初始化、双 Handler 管理、配置 API |
| **API Layer** | `Coredump.java` | `native*` 声明，建立 Java↔ Native 桥接 |
| **JNI Bridge** | `opencore_jni.cpp` | JNI 方法注册、分发到 Opencore C++ 层 |
| **Native Core** | `opencore.cpp`, `opencore.h` | 信号处理、ELF core 生成、架构特异性实现 |
| **Config Layer** | `build.gradle`, `CMakeLists.txt` | 编译配置、多架构支持 |
| **Test Layer** | `ExampleUnitTest.java`, `ExampleInstrumentedTest.java` | 单元测试和集成测试 |

---

## 3. 模块间依赖关系

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Java Layer"
        J1["Coredump.java<br/>单例模式"]
        J2["JavaCrashHandler<br/>实现 UncaughtExceptionHandler"]
        J3["OpencoreHandler<br/>Handler消息队列"]
        J4["OpencorePostHandler<br/>Handler消息队列"]
    end

    subgraph "Native Layer"
        N1["opencore_jni.cpp<br/>JNI桥接"]
        N2["opencore.cpp<br/>核心逻辑"]
        N3["arm64/opencore.cpp<br/>ARM64实现"]
        N4["lp64/opencore.h<br/>64位基类"]
    end

    J1 -->|"静态单例<br/>sInstance"| J1
    J1 -->|"sendEvent()"| J3
    J1 -->|"sendEvent()"| J4
    J1 -->|"waitCore/notifyCore"| J1
    J3 -->|"Message.obtain()"| J3
    J4 -->|"callbackEvent()"| J1
    J1 -->|"enable()"| J2
    J2 -->|"uncaughtException()"| J1
    J1 -.->|"JNI native*"| N1
    N1 -.->|"Opencore::"| N2
    N2 -.->|"继承链"| N3
    N2 -.->|"继承链"| N4
```

---

## 4. 五种设计模式

### 4.1 单例模式 - Coredump.java:29

```java
private static final Coredump sInstance = new Coredump();

public static Coredump getInstance() {
    return sInstance;
}
```

**意图**: 确保全局只有一个 `Coredump` 实例，所有线程共享相同状态。

---

### 4.2 观察者模式 - Listener 接口 onCompleted 回调

```java
public static interface Listener {
    void onCompleted(String path);
}

private Listener mListener;

public void setListener(Listener listener) {
    mListener = listener;
}

private void onCompleted(String filepath) {
    if (mListener != null) {
        mListener.onCompleted(filepath);
    }
}
```

**意图**: Java 层注册监听器，Native 层通过 `callbackEvent()` 回调通知 coredump 完成。

---

### 4.3 Handler消息队列 - OpencoreHandler / OpencorePostHandler

```java
private static class OpencoreHandler extends Handler {
    @Override
    public void handleMessage(Message msg) {
        switch (msg.what) {
            case CODE_COREDUMP: {
                Coredump.getInstance().nativeCoredump(msg.arg1, (String)msg.obj);
                Coredump.getInstance().notifyCore();  // 通知等待线程
            } break;
        }
    }
}
```

**意图**: Android Handler 机制实现异步消息处理，主线程通过 `waitCore()` 阻塞等待后台 Handler 完成。

---

### 4.4 模板方法 - JavaCrashHandler 实现 UncaughtExceptionHandler

```java
private static class JavaCrashHandler implements Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler {
    private Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler defaultHandler;

    public boolean enable() {
        defaultHandler = Thread.getDefaultUncaughtExceptionHandler();
        Thread.setDefaultUncaughtExceptionHandler(this);
        return true;
    }

    @Override
    public void uncaughtException(Thread thread, Throwable throwable) {
        try {
            disable();
            Coredump.getInstance().doCoredump();
        } finally {
            Process.killProcess(Process.myPid());
            System.exit(10);
        }
    }
}
```

**意图**: 模板方法模式，子类实现 `uncaughtException()` 钩子，在异常发生时自动触发 coredump。

---

### 4.5 生产者-消费者 - waitCore() / notifyCore() 同步

```java
private boolean waitCore() {
    synchronized (mLock) {
        while ((mCondition & COREDUMPED) != COREDUMPED)
            mLock.wait();
    }
    return true;
}

private void notifyCore() {
    synchronized (mLock) {
        mCondition |= COREDUMPED;
        mLock.notifyAll();
    }
}
```

**意图**: 使用 `Object.wait()/notifyAll()` 实现线程间同步，生产者（Handler）产生 `COREDUMPED` 信号，消费者（主线程）等待。

---

## 5. 数据流向图

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["doCoredump()<br/>Java API"] --> B["sendEvent<br/>CODE_COREDUMP"]
    B --> C["OpencoreHandler<br/>后台线程"]
    C --> D["nativeCoredump()<br/>JNI调用"]
    D --> E["Opencore::Dump()<br/>Native核心"]
    E --> F["fork() 创建子进程"]
    F --> G["DoCoredump()<br/>生成ELF Core"]
    G --> H["prctl PR_SET_DUMPABLE"]
    G --> I["ptrace PTRACE_ATTACH<br/>停止所有线程"]
    I --> J["WriteCoreHeader()<br/>ELF头部"]
    J --> K["WriteCorePrStatus()<br/>进程状态"]
    K --> L["WriteCoreTLS()<br/>线程本地存储"]
    L --> M["WriteCoreLoadSegment()<br/>内存段"]
    M --> N["callback()<br/>回调通知"]
    N --> O["callbackEvent()<br/>Java回调"]
    O --> P["OpencorePostHandler<br/>后处理线程"]
    P --> Q["onCompleted()<br/>通知Listener"]
    Q --> R["notifyCompleted()<br/>唤醒等待"]

    style G fill:#f9f,color:#000
    style N fill:#ff9,color:#000
```

### 同步时序

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as 主线程
    participant BG as OpencoreHandler
    participant Post as OpencorePostHandler
    participant Native as Opencore C++

    Main->>Main: doCoredump()
    Main->>BG: sendEvent(CODE_COREDUMP)
    Main->>Main: waitCore() [阻塞]

    BG->>Native: nativeCoredump()
    Native->>Native: fork() + DoCoredump()
    Native->>Native: 生成 core 文件
    Native->>BG: callbackEvent(filepath)

    BG->>Main: notifyCore() [唤醒]

    Main->>Post: sendEvent(CODE_COREDUMP_COMPLETED)
    Main->>Main: waitCompleted() [阻塞]

    Post->>Post: onCompleted()
    Post->>Main: notifyCompleted() [唤醒]

    Main->>Main: doCoredump() 返回
```

