## 8. 多线程同步机制

### 8.1 条件变量同步

```java
// mLock 作为锁对象
// mCondition 作为状态标志
private int mCondition = STANDBY;  // 0
private static final int COREDUMPED = 1 << 0;
private static final int COREDUMP_COMPLETED = 1 << 1;
```

### 8.2 同步流程

```mermaid
graph TD
    S["开始"] --> W1["waitCore()"]
    W1 --> C1{"mCondition &<br/>COREDUMPED?"}
    C1 -->|"否"| W1
    C1 -->|"是"| R1["返回 true"]

    S2["开始"] --> N1["notifyCore()"]
    N1 --> S1["mCondition |= COREDUMPED"]
    S1 --> N2["mLock.notifyAll()"]
    N2 --> E1["结束"]
```

### 8.3 Native 层互斥锁

```cpp
static pthread_mutex_t g_handle_lock = PTHREAD_MUTEX_INITIALIZER;
static pthread_mutex_t g_switch_lock = PTHREAD_MUTEX_INITIALIZER;

void Opencore::HandleSignal(int signal, siginfo_t* siginfo, void* ucontext_raw) {
    pthread_mutex_lock(&g_handle_lock);
    Disable();
    Dump(siginfo, ucontext_raw);
    raise(signal);
    pthread_mutex_unlock(&g_handle_lock);
}
```

